## 🎯 Objectives

* 📊 Understand Maps (dictionaries)
* 🎁 Work with tuples
* 🗂️ Organize complex data

## 🗺️ Maps - Like a Dictionary

```elixir
person = %{
  name: "Ana",
  age: 10,
  favorite_color: "blue"
}

IO.puts("Name: #{person.name}")
IO.puts("Age: #{person.age}")
IO.puts("Favorite color: #{person.favorite_color}")
```

## 🎁 Tuples - Ordered Groups

```elixir
coordinates = {10, 20}
{x, y} = coordinates

IO.puts("X: #{x}, Y: #{y}")
```

## 🎯 Your Turn

```elixir
my_profile = %{
  name: "Your name",
  age: 0,
  hobbies: ["...", "...", "..."],
  favorite: %{
    color: "...",
    animal: "..."
  }
}

Kino.Markdown.new("""
# #{my_profile.name}

**Age:** #{my_profile.age}

**Hobbies:** #{Enum.join(my_profile.hobbies, ", ")}

**Favorites:**
- Color: #{my_profile.favorite.color}
- Animal: #{my_profile.favorite.animal}
""")
```

